{"tid":1811700,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【中共報復】大陸擬取消買入捷克製飛機 抗議台捷關係升溫","createTime":"2020-01-05T02:29:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-05T06:05:04.000Z","uid":28765,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e5c93c936599a4fe3108324b552ff07d8cfe90ad","tid":1811700,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T02:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200105/large/1578184827_c2a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200105%2Flarge%2F1578184827_c2a9.jpg&h=d5763b55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大陸擬取消買入捷克製L-410短程飛機。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n大陸原本計劃向捷克購買30架的L-410客機，但鑑於捷克與台灣關係升溫，可能取消原本的買機計劃。<br />\n<br />\n捷克媒體Denik N2引述外交圈人士報道，總統齊曼（Milos Zeman）與眾議院議長馮德拉切克（Radek Vondracek）去年4月和11月訪問北京時，曾試圖說服大陸政府盡快完成L-410機型的認證，以促成交易，但中方至今沒有回應。<br />\n<br />\n雙引擎的短程飛機L-410是捷克重要的出口貨品，至今已生產1,000多架，大陸原本計劃向捷克購買30架。<br />\n<br />\n捷克總統府官員透露，大陸領導人對布拉格市長賀瑞普（Zdenek Hrib）和捷克參議院議長柯佳洛（Jaroslav Kubera）不滿，可能是這宗交易遲遲無法進行的原因。賀瑞普由於一中條款的爭議，去年10月解除與北京姊妹城市的關係，並準備在本月13日與到訪的台北市長柯文哲締結為姊妹城市，柯佳洛更打算在台灣總統大選過後訪台，兩者都是捷克與台灣關係升溫的訊號。<br />\n<br />\n捷克總統府對外辦公室主任金達拉克（Rudolf Jindrak）說：「大陸因為柯佳洛訪台而中斷這項交易，不是不可能的事。」報道還指，近年捷克與大陸的關係風波不斷。北京為了懲罰賀瑞普的友台立場，取消布拉格的樂團在大陸的巡迴演出，並中止深圳與布拉格的直航計劃。<br />\n此外，捷克情報機構警告大陸電訊設備製造商華為的安全性，也導致兩國關係緊張。<br />\n<br />\n中央社／捷克Denik N2<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20200105/60451644\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200105%2F60451644&d=x%2FFuRRgY0RqQB1T9iHKuLW6H7LaHGbUBdoVXdg05ZHE%3D&h=aa1cff5b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20200105%2F60451644&h=74b6040c\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20200105/60451644</a>"},{"pid":"123a03e1366f53dea112f25d6c2725178b488424","tid":1811700,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T02:32:02.000Z","msg":"自煮研發。"},{"pid":"dc16aaf8ed864748bee21180b73ab1cef0c4e319","tid":1811700,"uid":122940,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T02:33:03.000Z","msg":"避得幾多個，而且個個都針對佢"},{"pid":"c475c19edb27ca688f936b76d6531efd112dfb9c","tid":1811700,"uid":99172,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T02:33:28.000Z","msg":"冇錢買啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e75d73447bd146708a77becc2fcfa3f77ffca3b7","tid":1811700,"uid":8858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T02:34:36.000Z","msg":"全世界都對中共冷戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n強国自主燃發呀嘛，買咩外國貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0131cd3a0e6a5ef781f258b4c4a28088b62d74e6","tid":1811700,"uid":9315,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T02:34:43.000Z","msg":"1. 其實支那多數做樣  如果佢整到呀  一開頭就唔洗同你買啦<br />\n2. 更加說明依D朋友唔要都罷  睇住支那慢慢派錢比班非洲國家好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b24a2f6c8efee9ad0a448ce3e61b2cff39fcaac9","tid":1811700,"uid":298833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T02:38:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26b7718e58dd789611e97fd93bcddd5a1f424f96","tid":1811700,"uid":276175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T02:40:03.000Z","msg":"慳返d錢還債啦。"},{"pid":"afaee40983ef44ba342649b767c07de0da3432fe","tid":1811700,"uid":258731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T02:48:43.000Z","msg":"推到比立場/蘋果/議員睇到<br />\n［停止使用建制稱呼親共人士］<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZQscQho.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZQscQho.jpg&h=56da94ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n強烈要求使用「共派」取代「建制」稱呼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1811104\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.